\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Argument 1
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
1
\end_layout

\end_inset

Если 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{1}>p_{1}>1$
\end_inset

, то 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{p_{2}}\vkl L_{p_{1}}\vkl L_{1}$
\end_inset

.
